author: StevenTheBrick
title: The End Battle
review:
5/5

This is an example of a perfect Lego Set.

The price is absolutely worth it. The parts are great, which are used for the Ender Dragon and the End section. The building experience was awesome. The playability gets a lot of points due to the Ender Dragon being able to shoot spring-loaded misses in a way that won't lose them or shoot them easily. The movement is also great for the Ender Dragon.
